<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1">
    <title>Sorry...页面没有找到</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="__ADMIN__/layui/css/layui.css">
    <style>
        body{
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .layui-container{
            height: 560px;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            margin: auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            color: #393d49;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        .layui-icon{
            font-size: 360px;
            display: block;
        }
        .layui-word-aux{
            margin: 15px;
        }
        @media screen and (max-width:768px) {
            body {
                background-color: #fff;
            }
            .layui-container{
                height: 500px;
            }
            .layui-icon{
                font-size: 300px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="layui-container">
        <div class="layui-row">
            <div class="layui-col-md12">
                <i class="layui-icon layui-icon-404"></i>
                <h1>Sorry...页面没有找到</h1>
                <p class="layui-word-aux">似乎你所寻找的网页已移动或丢失了</p>
                <a href="/" class="layui-btn layui-btn-lg layui-btn-primary">返回首页</a>
                <a href="/" class="layui-btn layui-btn-lg">反馈错误</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
